<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/24580127">游戏的大小和游戏画质有绝对关系吗？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2014158" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">为什么一些画质很差的国产网游也要好几个G？而几乎相同大小的国外游戏，画质则要好的多？是优化的关系吗？还是因为网游的元素比较多的关系？</div>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-meta zm-item-comment-el clearfix" id="zh-question-meta-wrap">
<div class="zm-meta-panel">

