<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$meng-de-er" href="/people/meng-de-er">孟德尔</a>，<strong title="不玩游戏的游戏迷" class="zu-question-my-bio">不玩游戏的游戏迷</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="15">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$li-shi-chao-99" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/li-shi-chao-99" class="zg-link" title="李世超">李世超</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$deviluvatar" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/deviluvatar" class="zg-link" title="白浪巅儿">白浪巅儿</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


